      "text": {
        "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Problem\">Problem</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/wiki/index.php?title=1991_APMO_Problems/Problem_3&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Problem\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Let <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/1/a/b/1ab39d761413804680d26d972381f028001562f5.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$a_1$\" style=\"vertical-align: -2px\" width=\"15\" height=\"10\" />, <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/5/e/9/5e97a8af68fbc8e357d3ee0eba452022b06c1875.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$a_2$\" style=\"vertical-align: -2px\" width=\"15\" height=\"10\" />, <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/0/8/7/087594ea26fa196b8e61bc20a36228270dc695f8.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\cdots$\" style=\"vertical-align: 3px\" width=\"19\" height=\"2\" />, <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/6/f/1/6f1a2b6b7c193f9ba2b2134a59f1da5addcfbc98.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$a_n$\" style=\"vertical-align: -2px\" width=\"17\" height=\"10\" />, <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/6/9/f/69fc4b9ed6d75d026557e7b06c2ed483c6ed0eda.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$b_1$\" style=\"vertical-align: -2px\" width=\"13\" height=\"15\" />, <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/9/3/b/93b7aa611365e135f58aa09d52043ecd34855fe4.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$b_2$\" style=\"vertical-align: -2px\" width=\"14\" height=\"15\" />, <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/0/8/7/087594ea26fa196b8e61bc20a36228270dc695f8.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\cdots$\" style=\"vertical-align: 3px\" width=\"19\" height=\"2\" />, <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/8/f/f/8ffd01cdc48042ce7c67d8edcd4904809831cfe4.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$b_n$\" style=\"vertical-align: -2px\" width=\"16\" height=\"15\" /> be positive real numbers such that <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/5/2/e/52e68691bb89ed51db4c551786c5db353406ed36.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$a_1 + a_2 + \\cdots + a_n = b_1 + b_2 + \\cdots + b_n$\" style=\"vertical-align: -2px\" width=\"299\" height=\"15\" />.  Show that \n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/0/f/4/0f4985029cc0227d46a829d94c18ab1432ac8dc6.png\" class=\"latexcenter\" alt=\"\\[\\frac{a_1^2}{a_1 + b_1} + \\frac{a_2^2}{a_2 + b_2} + \\cdots + \\frac{a_n^2}{a_n + b_n} \\geq \\frac{a_1 + a_2 + \\cdots + a_n}{2}\\]\" width=\"432\" height=\"41\" />\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Solution\">Solution</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/wiki/index.php?title=1991_APMO_Problems/Problem_3&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Solution\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>By Cauchy-Schwarz, <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/4/4/5/445f54e928e9ca04ce25860db9a009ab91718a4e.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\left(\\sum \\dfrac{a_i^2}{a_i+b_i}\\right)\\left(\\sum a_i+b_i\\right)\\geq \\left(\\sum a_i\\right) ^2$\" style=\"vertical-align: -17px\" width=\"308\" height=\"43\" />. Since <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/5/9/8/5983c2cf2ac4403ee651f495cc180968da3d406b.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\sum a_i=\\sum b_i$\" style=\"vertical-align: -8px\" width=\"109\" height=\"25\" />, we get<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/b/0/0/b00e8a2e8791f25518eb93f9daefbff6209acb96.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\sum \\dfrac{a_i^2}{a_i+b_i}\\geq \\dfrac{\\left(\\sum a_i\\right) ^2}{\\sum (a_i+b_i)}=\\dfrac{\\sum a_i}{2}$\" style=\"vertical-align: -17px\" width=\"258\" height=\"46\" />.\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240907082555\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.011 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.011 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 105/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 272/1000000\nPost窶親xpand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighe